OL,3,CSentencing Bill to be introduced
OL,4,Cshortly, Justice Minister says
OL,6,FA Sentencing Bill which would see
OL,7,Flonger time in jail for killers who
OL,8,Fdecline to disclose their victims'
OL,9,Fbodies whereabouts will be introduced
OL,10,Fto the Assembly, Justice Minister
OL,11,FNaomi Long has said.
OL,13,FThe Bill, which includes significant
OL,14,Freforms to sentencing policy, will
OL,15,Falso create a new offence for those
OL,16,Fwho assault police officers or others
OL,17,Fproviding a public service.
