OL,3,CSentencing Bill to be introduced
OL,4,Cshortly, Justice Minister says
OL,6,FMs Long said the legislation will have
OL,7,F"a positive impact on the lives of
OL,8,Fthousands of people across Northern
OL,9,FIreland."
OL,11,FShe added: "It will increase the
OL,12,Fmaximum penalty for causing death, or
OL,13,Fserious injury by dangerous driving or
OL,14,Fcareless driving whilst under the
OL,15,Finfluence of drink or drugs, from 14
OL,16,Fyears to 20 years.
OL,18,F"It will also introduce a new offence
OL,19,Fand higher sentences for assaulting
OL,20,Fthose providing a service to the
OL,21,Fpublic or performing a public duty.
