OL,3,CSentencing Bill to be introduced
OL,4,Cshortly, Justice Minister says
OL,6,F"The Bill will also create
OL,7,F'Charlotte's Law', which aims to
OL,8,Freduce the trauma experienced by
OL,9,Ffamilies of murder victims in so
OL,10,Fcalled 'no body' cases."
OL,12,FThe law is named after Charlotte
OL,13,FMurray, who was murdered by her former
OL,14,Fpartner Johnny Miller.
OL,16,FMs Murray went missing in 2012 and her
OL,17,Fbody has never been found.
