OL,3,CSentencing Bill to be introduced
OL,4,Cshortly, Justice Minister says
OL,6,FIt will see the creation of a
OL,7,Fstatutory aggravator for failure to
OL,8,Fdisclose the location of victims'
OL,9,Fremains and new sentence reductions
OL,10,Ffor post-sentence disclosures.
OL,12,FIt will also introduce provisions
OL,13,Fequivalent to Helen's Law in England
OL,14,Fand Wales, requiring Parole
OL,15,FCommissioners to consider failure to
OL,16,Fdisclose the location of victims'
OL,17,Fremains in release decisions.
