OL,3,CSentencing Bill to be introduced
OL,4,Cshortly, Justice Minister says
OL,6,FMs Long said: "In developing this
OL,7,FBill, I have met and listened to a
OL,8,Frange of victims and stakeholder
OL,9,Forganisations.
OL,11,F"Their voices have been crucial and as
OL,12,Fwe move closer to introducing the
OL,13,FSentencing Bill."
OL,15,FThe bill will also set statutory
OL,16,Fstarting points for life sentence
OL,17,Ftariffs for murder cases, with 15
OL,18,Fyears as the starting point where
OL,19,Fthere are no significant aggravating
OL,20,Ffeatures and 20 years for the worst
OL,21,Fcases.
